reviewText: Not as much history as I was lead to believe from the promo msyerial

I grew up in California during the 70s and 80s and this video is a great look back at life before the mega mergers.  Like the combination of 90s video and earlier film.

There is some coverage from areas pretty far from tehachapi, but that was not a drawback to me.
Nicely done, great footage.  The only sad note is that you can no longer go up to the loop without probably getting fined by Railroad Police - a sad comment on our society.
